Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.06,0:00:35.10,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:05.61,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:17.86,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.77,0:22:54.81,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.47,0:24:09.51,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Epilogue}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.48,0:24:16.52,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.61,0:00:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Velvet Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid my master is away today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.45,0:00:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Or did you perchance intentionally come while he's out?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you have obtained yet another Arcana: the Emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.88,0:00:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder just how far your unparalleled Persona abilities will evolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.38,0:00:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}I daresay you have piqued my curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's hot out, you gotta match it with hot cup noodles!{why, chie? why?}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice and sultry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.04,0:02:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta fight fire with fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't this rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What does?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.09,0:02:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer clothes rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.88,0:02:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a perverted look in your eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.26,0:02:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You sound like a creep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.76,0:02:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up! He was looking too! Why are you guys only attacking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, moving on...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We should watch TV every night once the rainy season hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.19,0:02:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the Midnight Channel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be getting tons of rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.40,0:02:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But I hope it's nice out this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The school camping trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The day before the school camping trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.42,0:03:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this your guys' first school camping trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Each team has to prepare their own meals, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard all about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we make?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.51,0:03:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I was debating between noodles and curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I prefer curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then curry it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't forget about my opinion!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Curry! We gotta do curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Camping equals curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.02,0:03:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, we get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Carrots, potatoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you do on the trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.61,0:03:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We just pick up trash in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.74,0:03:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What, seriously? No one told me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the other stuff is kinda fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.41,0:03:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We get to cook outside and sleep in tents.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The four of us make one team, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.25,0:03:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So do we share a tent?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys and girls sleep separately!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,After we were dismissed, though, didn't we go play by the riverbank?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, we did!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.93,0:04:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You can swim in the river?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess so. People did it in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.81,0:04:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I just remembered something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What about the shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.44,0:04:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}At Junes, every day is Customer Appreciation Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where'd they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They're still shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Come see for yourself, and get in touch with our products!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I bet we're in good hands with Amagi around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Every day's great at your Junes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, she's the future manager of a traditional inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.54,0:04:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Junes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Every day's great at your Junes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so jealous! You were at Junes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I went shopping there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I picked up dinner while I was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ingredients to make curry for the school camping trip and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Curry? That sounds yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:05:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I love curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.28,0:05:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be out all day tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.95,0:05:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.12,0:05:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can watch the house by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,With a red rose in my right hand and a silk hat in my left,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,my codename is Magical Experiment X!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd you do that? Again! Do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,School camping trip, day one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.41,0:05:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Cu-Cu-Cu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Culicid?{stupid japanese puns. Culicid/culicidae means mosquitoes, which is explained later, i guess.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.08,0:05:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,W-W-Wa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Worms?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mosquitoes and worms?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There weren't any in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness! I was afraid some fell in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:06:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Hanamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:06:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You know how cooking outside can attract insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see what's so funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the curry too spicy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's mild.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you, Chie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah! If you're so worried, why don't you try some?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea! Why don't you give it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.62,0:06:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.25,0:06:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell did you—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we should've taste-tested it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have the courage to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Curry's supposed to be really spicy or kinda mild!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But that thing just stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's somehow both gritty and slimy! And it's got squishy parts too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.52,0:06:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so frickin' nasty I can't even swallow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it just didn't mix too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.86,0:07:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But we put a lot of love into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell kind of "love" did you put in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Curry uses cornstarch, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, it wouldn't thicken up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So I guess we'll need cornstarch and flour.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we use strong or weak flour?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Strong, of course. We're feeding boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.38,0:07:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...is red peppers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not curry if it isn't spicy hot. {someone missed the word "if"}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing has spicy in the name! Oh, and pepper!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.14,0:07:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Pepper comes in black and white.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the manager's daughter for ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now for something to bring out the flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I heard on TV to mix in coffee!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But I hate coffee, so let's use coffee {\i1}milk{\i0} instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.49,0:07:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How about sea cucumber? It'll give us a good broth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.49,0:07:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Get anything that sounds about right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what? Our team's gonna starve!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, if it was even slightly edible...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not taking another bite of Mystery Food X.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.34,0:08:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That curry looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Ohtani?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those leftovers?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got a new twist!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So is it true Konishi doesn't have to do any homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what? I'm so jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no wonder, considering what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.83,0:08:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The poor guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I help out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay! Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.63,0:08:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm part of the health association.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. We have everything covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about participating in the camping trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you busy helping around home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.89,0:08:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna help pick up trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll join you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Konishi, you can stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but he needs an antacid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.62,0:09:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My stomach's killing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.26,0:09:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Konishi Naoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.97,0:09:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate Hanamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He's Konishi's little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.44,0:09:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We talked a couple times when I was with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend told me he's been alone a lot since the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.45,0:09:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.45,0:09:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:09:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the bowls here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.71,0:10:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks again, Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm amazed you found us out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We might order dinner from you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nice! You ordered delivery!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are so thoughtful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.39,0:10:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We just ordered whatever, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat up before King Moron finds us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what exactly are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My teachers threatened to hold me back a year if I skipped the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.53,0:10:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But the freshmen tent is so quiet you'd think someone died there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I bet it is when you're around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.12,0:10:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I prefer being with you guys, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know Konishi Naoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki, huh? Sure, I know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We're childhood friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What— For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...Konishi's little brother, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:11:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We hung out a lot back in elementary school,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but we haven't talked much lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he like in class?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.73,0:11:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true he's always being left out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.86,0:11:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You "dunno"?! This is important!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know! We're in different classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you're no help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Dude, you're the annoying one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.21,0:11:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Done already?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.38,0:11:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to learn more about him, just ask him directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But that wasn't the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, wh-what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you being left out in class?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's {\i1}too{\i0} direct!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the first time someone's asked me that straight to my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's actually refreshing for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:12:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true. Honestly, I feel left out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like everyone's staring at me from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They're always babying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.75,0:12:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been skipping school a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I have to help my family fend off the press and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.09,0:12:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how you feel. I have to do the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, the neighbors have been coming to take shifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.93,0:12:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They tell me to live my life to the fullest for my sister and then start crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.23,0:12:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's suffocating.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.69,0:12:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's yours if you want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? A beef bowl from Aiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.03,0:12:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure? That's my favorite!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.53,0:12:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Those are my seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just deal with it, Kanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Be nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Punk, you owe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm sorry I said I hated you when I didn't even know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.67,0:12:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I kinda had fun today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hang out again sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.30,0:12:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.93,0:13:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta catch the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Deduction time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanji's incident disproved our idea that all the victims would be women.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.63,0:13:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We might be overlooking something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that I can think of any other connection...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.97,0:13:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try to come up with something, anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom told me that after Councilman Namatame got fired,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.48,0:13:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,he came back here and inherited his family's business.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that too. Isn't he a deliveryman now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't he have a fling with Ms. Yamano?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:14:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder he got kicked off the council.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But didn't he have an alibi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't seem like our guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Actually, I think I got something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember how Ms. Yamano appeared on the news over her affair?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And Konishi was on the news as the one who found the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.51,0:14:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Amagi, weren't you interviewed on TV, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.97,0:14:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And wasn't Kanji on some special?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I wish I could forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then everyone appeared on TV before they vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt it's a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.11,0:14:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's related to the TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.82,0:14:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So our culprit's gonna go after the next person featured on TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.12,0:14:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's highly likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But who would do this, and why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no idea as to what his motives are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:15:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, punks! Quit yer yapping and pick up the damn trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, pay close attention to whoever's on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to stay on our toes and check out a bunch of channels.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,School camping trip at night... night... night...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So do you really swing that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What way?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering our situation, I'd like you to be honest with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.25,0:15:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is our chastity in danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the hell?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why the extreme reaction?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It only makes you seem more suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.47,0:15:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with women now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.72,0:15:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't fully trust you, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleeping next to you takes courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.77,0:15:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, didn't you accept me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.73,0:15:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to the girls' tent!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll prove I'm a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate the great Tatsumi Kanji, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.62,0:16:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get expelled if King Moron finds out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.59,0:16:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Will she stop snoring if we cover her nose and mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Bear-sona!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.61,0:16:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't go back to our tent!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.53,0:16:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, Kanji, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.91,0:16:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He burst in and fell unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Yukiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.37,0:16:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:16:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn’t sleep with him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He could go berserk when he wakes up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I don't have my shit list on hand...{king moron}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's King Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hide already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}but anyone caught doing anything inappropriate
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Under here for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.39,0:17:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}is getting their asses kicked outta school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.85,0:17:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're too close, Hanamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.48,0:17:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Keep that in mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep quiet, stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you asleep in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You two better answer if you're in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're not! Shut the hell up and go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit, I drank too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Years were just shaved off my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't go out right now, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.14,0:18:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll leave before anyone wakes up, so can we please stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.44,0:18:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see why not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay out of our side, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.11,0:18:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do anything weird, Hanamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Come again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay with this arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.87,0:18:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.04,0:18:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.63,0:18:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That night was uncomfortable in more ways than one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,School camping trip, day two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.08,0:19:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.33,0:19:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The trip was over before we knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great that no one got expelled?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.67,0:19:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.34,0:19:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All righty then!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're all here, let's go swimming!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.72,0:19:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.18,0:19:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you're going swimming?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pass. I'm way too tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.35,0:19:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you able to get any sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't sleep with anyone or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.44,0:19:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.19,0:19:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But it wouldn't be any fun if I swam alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you looking at? Go swim by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you two still owe us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, we do owe you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! We didn't bring our swimsuits!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Yukiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, it really is unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.34,0:19:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They're Junes-brand originals! Just in for the summer season!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.39,0:20:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.39,0:20:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you went to get?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, that's messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They're taking forever! How far out did they go to change?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, those swim trunks are awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren’t they hip?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They sure are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.33,0:20:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit staring at us! It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.71,0:20:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You two look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.09,0:20:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you have to go and say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, you're hotter than I imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Those girls might be childish on the inside, but I bet they're gonna turn into some fine-looking women!{hopefully not 3 lines}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Narukami?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.94,0:20:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.94,0:20:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys crossed the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:20:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Kanji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to push us in!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares? You were going in, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.97,0:21:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.52,0:21:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,King Moron?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I drank too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yikes! Something's floating downstream!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.11,0:21:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.87,0:21:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I stink?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.91,0:21:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say another word.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We've lost something important again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:21:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing we found out before we got in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.38,0:21:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:21:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.88,0:22:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.14,0:22:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.81,0:22:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...confess her feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.02,0:22:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.03,0:22:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.49,0:22:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.33,0:22:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.75,0:22:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,aren't my type.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.25,0:22:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.88,0:22:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just forget about last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.39,0:22:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.73,0:22:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let's leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.47,0:24:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.81,0:24:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.44,0:24:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I might get kidnapped, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.94,0:24:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.82,0:24:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! That ain't cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.19,0:24:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiraiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.86,0:24:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be the culprit's warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.95,0:24:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
